WEBVTT

00:00:01.707 --> 00:00:04.596
Nyumbani, watu huniita mpiga makelele,

00:00:04.596 --> 00:00:07.313
mleta matata, msumbufu,

00:00:07.313 --> 00:00:09.983
muasi, mwanaharakati,

00:00:09.983 --> 00:00:11.840
kioo cha jamii.

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.010
Lakini sikuwa hivyo.

00:00:14.650 --> 00:00:16.182
Utotoni, nilikuwa na jina la utani.

00:00:16.182 --> 00:00:18.502
Waliniita Softi,

00:00:18.502 --> 00:00:21.755
yaani kijana mwepesi asiye na mambo mengi.

00:00:21.755 --> 00:00:24.495
Kama binaadamu yeyote, niliepuka balaa,

00:00:24.495 --> 00:00:26.538
Utotoni, walinifunza kimya.

00:00:26.538 --> 00:00:28.449
Usibishane, fanya unachoambiwa.

00:00:28.449 --> 00:00:30.360
Kwenye shule ya dini, walinifunza 
nisilete bughudha, nisibishane.